<section id="overview">
      <h2>Year Overview</h2>
      <p>The Dog (<span class="chinese-char">狗</span>) occupies the Earthly Branch <strong>Xu (戌)</strong>, carrying Yang Earth energy with hidden Metal and Fire. In 2026, the Dog is a key member of the <strong>Yin-Wu-Xu Fire Triangle</strong> (寅午戌三合火局), one of the four San He combinations and among the most powerful harmonies in Chinese astrology.</p>
      <p>This triangle means the Dog is in <strong>profound alignment with the year's energy</strong>. Fire Horse energy flows through the triangle and generates the Dog's Earth element, creating a year of warmth, support, and practical achievement. The Dog's characteristic loyalty, sense of justice, and protective nature are recognised and valued.</p>
      <p>The Dog also carries hidden Fire within its branch (丁 Ding, Yin Fire), which resonates with the year's Fire energy. This internal-external alignment creates <strong>authenticity and confidence</strong> — the Dog feels more comfortable in its own skin than in many previous years. Decisions come naturally, and the Dog's moral compass is well-calibrated.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="fire-triangle">
      <h2>The Tiger-Horse-Dog Fire Triangle (寅午戌三合)</h2>
      <div class="callout-box callout-box--jade">
        <div class="callout-icon">🔥</div>
        <div class="callout-content">
          <h3>San He Fire Trinity</h3>
          <p>The Dog (Xu/戌) completes the <strong>San He fire triangle</strong> (三合火局) together with the Tiger (Yin/寅) and Horse (Wu/午). As the <strong>storage phase</strong> of fire, the Dog's Earth energy receives, grounds, and preserves the fire generated by the Tiger-Horse axis.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>In 2026, a Horse year, the Dog benefits enormously from this triangle. While the Tiger initiates fire and the Horse carries it, the Dog <strong>stores and stabilises</strong> it. In classical five-phase theory, Fire generates Earth — meaning the year's dominant energy directly nourishes the Dog's core element. This is one of the most favourable positions in the zodiac cycle.</p>
      <p>What the fire triangle means for Dog-born people in 2026:</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><strong>Recognition and reward</strong> — years of loyal effort are finally acknowledged; promotions, awards, and public appreciation are strongly indicated</li>
        <li><strong>Peak months</strong> — February (Tiger month) and October (Dog month) activate the full triangle, creating exceptional windows for achievement</li>
        <li><strong>Grounding role</strong> — others look to you for stability and reliability; embrace this role rather than seeking the spotlight</li>
        <li><strong>Tiger allies</strong> — collaboration with Tiger-born people completes two-thirds of the triangle and creates powerful synergy</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Classical insight:</strong> The Dog as fire's <em>storage</em> (墓庫) phase means you absorb the year's passionate energy and convert it to lasting achievement. The Dog's virtue of loyalty (義, <em>yi</em>) is the bridge that transforms volatile fire into enduring warmth.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="career">
      <h2>Career &amp; Finance</h2>
      <p>Career prospects are <strong>strongly favourable</strong>. The fire triangle's support means the Dog is in the right place at the right time — promotions, new responsibilities, and leadership opportunities arrive through natural progression rather than aggressive pursuit. The Dog's reliability and ethical standards attract the trust of superiors and colleagues.</p>
      <p><strong>Finance</strong> benefits from stable career growth and the Earth element's strengthened position. Property purchases, long-term investments, and building financial security are all well-timed. The Dog's natural caution with money serves well — avoid being drawn into others' speculative schemes during Fire months.</p>
      <p><strong>Best sectors:</strong> Law, justice system, social work, non-profit, security, veterinary, public service, human resources, and any field where integrity and loyalty are primary assets.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="love">
      <h2>Love &amp; Relationships</h2>
      <p>The fire triangle's warmth creates <strong>deep emotional security</strong> that benefits all relationships. The Dog's partner experiences a warmer, more confident, and more expressive version of the normally reserved Dog. Commitments made in 2026 — engagements, marriages, moving in together — are well-starred.</p>
      <p><strong>Single Dogs</strong> benefit from the increased confidence and social visibility that the fire triangle provides. The Rabbit (secret friend) provides gentle romantic connections, while the Tiger months (February) brings bold, exciting possibilities. The Dog's genuine, unpretentious nature attracts sincere partners who value character over flash.</p>
      <p><strong>Friendships</strong> deepen significantly. The Dog's loyalty circle strengthens, and new friendships formed through shared values or community service become important long-term bonds.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="health">
      <h2>Health &amp; Wellness</h2>
      <p>The Dog's health is <strong>generally robust</strong> in 2026, supported by the fire triangle's balanced energy. The main risk is excess Earth leading to digestive heaviness or overthinking — the Dog's tendency to worry about others can become chronic anxiety if unchecked.</p>
      <p><strong>Stomach and spleen</strong> benefit from regular meals and warm, nourishing food. The Dog should avoid skipping meals during busy periods — blood sugar drops amplify the Dog's natural anxiety.</p>
      <p><strong>Outdoor exercise</strong> is ideal: hiking, running, team sports, and activities with dogs or other animals. The Dog draws energy from nature and physical community. Guard duty (literally or metaphorically) is the Dog's comfort zone — volunteering for night walks, neighbourhood watch, or similar protective activities satisfies the Dog's deep need for purpose.</p>
    </section>

